恥ずかしい?

11
00:01:41,515 --> 00:01:42,180
It's embarrassing.
恥ずかしい

12
00:01:42,180 --> 00:01:44,000
what are you doing
何してる

13
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,000
of?
の?

14
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,320
I still feel like I haven't seen enough.
まだ 見足りないなと思って

15
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:23,005
I can't let you go home yet.
まだ帰らせないよ

16
00:02:23,005 --> 00:02:24,720
